```class Solution {
    public long minSumSquareDiff(int[] nums1, int[] nums2, int k1, int k2) {
        int n = nums1.length;
        long res = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            long diff = (long) (nums1[i] - nums2[i]);
            res += diff * diff;
            if (k1 > 0) {
                res -= 2 * diff;
                k1--;
            }
            if (k2 > 0) {
                res -= 2 * diff;
                k2--;
            }
        }
        return res;
    }
}```
